title: Chris Russell at The Nude Bowl
description: It began as a hideout for Al Capone, and became the location for a surrounding Nude Colony. Since the late 70's the Nude Bowl has brought skaters near & far to make it to the deep and scrape cope on some of the crustiest pool terrain around. Resurrection!! Get some, Chris!
